## Phased Implementation Approach

For complex Level 3 and 4 tasks, follow a phased implementation:

### Phase 1: Core Implementation
- Implement foundational components
- Build essential interfaces
- Establish primary data models
- Create main service structure

### Phase 2: Supporting Features
- Implement secondary functionality
- Build utility components
- Create supporting services
- Develop extension points

### Phase 3: Integrations
- Connect with other components
- Implement API endpoints
- Build UI integrations
- Create necessary adapters

### Phase 4: Refinement (Level 4 only)
- Optimize performance
- Enhance error handling
- Improve usability
- Complete end-to-end testing

