## Implementation Checklist

- [ ] Review implementation plan thoroughly
- [ ] Understand existing code structure
- [ ] Verify all dependencies are available
- [ ] Create scaffolding/structure first
- [ ] Follow phased implementation approach
- [ ] Write tests alongside implementation
- [ ] Document code as you write it
- [ ] Check for edge cases
- [ ] Ensure error handling is robust
- [ ] Run linters and formatters
- [ ] Update relevant documentation
- [ ] Perform final testing
- [ ] Update task status

## Transition to Reflection Mode

Once implementation is complete:
1. Ensure all tests pass
2. Verify all documentation is updated
3. Address any TODO items
4. Update implementation status in tasks.md
5. Transition to Reflection Mode for review and refinement
